biweekly.property

Class VCalAlarmProperty

  • java.lang.Object
    • biweekly.property.ICalProperty
      • biweekly.property.VCalAlarmProperty
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AudioAlarm, DisplayAlarm, EmailAlarm, ProcedureAlarm

    public class VCalAlarmProperty
extends ICalProperty

    Defines an alarm property that is part of the vCalendar (1.0) standard (such as AudioAlarm).

    Classes that extend this class are used internally by this library for parsing purposes. If you are creating a new iCalendar object and need to define an alarm, it is recommended that you use the VAlarm component to create a new alarm.

    Author:
    Michael Angstadt
    See Also:
    vCal 1.0
